      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p><br/><br/>The <em>lightlinker </em>node allows you to control the object and light-specific workflows for both light and shadow linking in your Solaris scene. <br/>This adds extra creative control and refinement for your RenderMan lights in Solaris.</p><p><br/><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544641475/RenderMan_Solaris_LightLinking_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433089452&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544641475/RenderMan_Solaris_LightLinking_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433089452&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544641489\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_LightLinking_1.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544641475\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"204977e6-0b48-41a1-82f5-8bfc5e6042d9\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/><br/>For more detailed information on using the <em>lightlinker </em>node in Solaris, please consult the SideFx docs,<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.sidefx.com/docs/houdini/nodes/lop/lightlinker.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"> linked here</a></p>"
    }
